data.description: *** Price below appraisal! *** Amazing 6 bed/4.5 bath home features 2 full owner's suites, 2 year new HVAC, 2 ''hidden'' rooms, wet bar w/ Kegerator, detached 30X50 workshop (5 total garage bays inc attached garage) & RV hookup. You're greeted by spacious living areas w/ beautiful hardwood floors & stone fireplace. The kitchen features a walk-in pantry, industrial grade appliances, copper range hood & new butcher block counters. The primary Owner's Suite features double sinks, soaking tub, walk-in closet, fireplace & hidden storage room. Outside you'll enjoy a sparkling pool, built-in BBQ, raised garden, full size covered patio & balcony w/ incredible views! Plus a huge laundry room w/ lots of storage, horse corral & nearby hiking trails. Come & check out this entertainer's dream.
